00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:15,640
- You know, Toppy.
- Topol.

157
00:10:15,680 --> 00:10:18,280
Yes, that's right.
Topol.

158
00:10:18,360 --> 00:10:20,200
Mm-hmm.

159
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:24,000
Actually, Ringo Starr doesn't--
doesn't look at all like, uh, Topol.

160
00:10:24,040 --> 00:10:27,001
Yeah, but he was--
he was quite a long way away from me.

161
00:10:27,081 --> 00:10:30,041
So actually it could've
been neither of them.

162
00:10:30,121 --> 00:10:32,881
Yes, I suppose so, yes.

163
00:10:32,961 --> 00:10:37,161
- It's not a classic anecdote, is it?
- Not a classic, no. No.

164
00:10:40,801 --> 00:10:45,081
- Another one?
- [ Sighs ] Yes. No.

165
00:10:45,121 --> 00:10:48,441
Let's go crazy.
I'll have an orange juice.

166
00:10:48,521 --> 00:10:51,361
