167
00:10:53,761 --> 00:10:56,442
- Okay, thanks. Bye-bye.
- See you later.

168
00:11:03,082 --> 00:11:05,042
- Oh!
- Oh! Shit!

169
00:11:05,122 --> 00:11:07,962
- Oh, my God!
- Bugger! I'm so sorry. I'm so sorry.

170
00:11:08,042 --> 00:11:10,802
- Here. Let me--
- Get your hands off!

171
00:11:10,882 --> 00:11:13,562
I'm really sorry.
I- I live just over the street.

172
00:11:13,602 --> 00:11:16,722
I have, um, water and soap.
