as it normally is, I fear.

183
00:11:57,844 --> 00:12:00,884
But, um--
The bathroom's on the top floor.

184
00:12:00,924 --> 00:12:04,644
And the telephone's just--
just up here.

185
00:12:06,164 --> 00:12:08,404
Here.
Let-- Let me, um--

186
00:12:13,964 --> 00:12:17,244
Um, round the corner.
Straight on-- straight on up.

187
00:12:20,925 --> 00:12:22,765
Bugger.

188
00:12:23,965 --> 00:12:25,845
[ Groans ]

189
