before you go?

192
00:12:46,645 --> 00:12:48,885
- No.
- Coffee?

193
00:12:48,966 --> 00:12:51,606
- No.
- Orange juice?

194
00:12:52,726 --> 00:12:57,006
Probably not.
Um, something else cold.

195
00:12:57,086 --> 00:12:58,926
