with fruits of the forest?

199
00:13:07,006 --> 00:13:09,966
- No.
- Would you like something to eat?

200
00:13:10,046 --> 00:13:12,206
Uh, something to nibble?

201
00:13:12,286 --> 00:13:15,966
Um, apricots soaked in honey?

202
00:13:16,046 --> 00:13:19,327
